{"tid":1257574,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"michael jackson入唔到20世紀風雲人物 ?","createTime":"2019-06-25T15:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T16:48:24.000Z","uid":70760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"631380c2dc84d9faf82390d170851150f66e4d15","tid":1257574,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3100%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E6%9C%80%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2597%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A3100%25E4%25BA%25BA%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%25BA%25AA%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%25A9&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=e7c120c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3100%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E6%9C%80%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9</a>"},{"pid":"1e2433bb57fed8b88eaf107ac72adc70b5acc6ec","tid":1257574,"uid":232575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"時代雜誌條list有好多偏見<br />\n嗰個Brues 話貓王係純表演者，而唔係思想形創作人所以唔入選。咁就唔應該入馬龍百蘭度。攞明係quota 制行先。估計時代第一標準係「(演藝人)喺1999年嗰一刻，己經對社會作出咗二三十年既改變」即係八、九十年代人物會先扣分。<br />\n<br />\n全list只有幾個人發跡期係喺八、九十年代之後，而嗰幾個人唔洗經歷時間洗禮同證明，己經充分表現到個人影響力。例如bill gate。或者係政治(加分)考慮例如六四坦克人。<br />\n<br />\nMichael Jackson輸既原因大致係，第一係MJ喺80年代先進入頂峰而且係唱作男人(所以個qouta 去咗60年代Bob Dylan到)、第二係MJ係90年代有metoo醜聞(條list 99年出)、第三係黑白色人種「爭議」<br />\n<br />\n如果條list 2050年先出，對mj 會公平啲，都好大機會入選。<br />\n條條list標準唔同，我相信mj 可以入到大部分標準既list。"}]}